### **Buy-Back Summary (Appendix 3C - Equal Access Scheme)**  

- **Security:** LF1 (Ordinary Units)  
- **Buy-Back Type:** Equal access scheme (5% of issued units)  
- **Total Buy-Back Volume:** 7.5M units (~5% of 150M on issue)  
- **Pricing:** NAV per unit (calculated at Buy-Back Pricing Date) + accrued distributions  
- **Key Dates:**  
  - **Ex-Date:** 13/8/2025  
  - **Record Date:** 14/8/2025  
  - **Offer Close:** 11/9/2025  
  - **Settlement:** 15/9/2025  
- **Scale-Back:** Pro rata if oversubscribed.  
- **Foreign Participation:** Excludes non-Australian/NZ holders.
